<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Action<sp/>and<sp/>observation<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>any<sp/>arbitrary<sp/>type,<sp/>whatever<sp/>is<sp/>needed<sp/>for<sp/>your</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">robot.<sp/><sp/>There<sp/>are<sp/>only<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>restrictions:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>If<sp/>you<sp/>want<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>the<sp/>@ref<sp/>robot_interfaces::MultiProcessRobotData,<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
