<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>[cereal](https://uscilab.github.io/cereal/).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>If<sp/>you<sp/>want<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>the<sp/>@ref<sp/>robot_interfaces::RobotLogger,<sp/>the<sp/>action<sp/>and</highlight></codeline>
