<codeline><highlight class="normal">robot_interfaces::RobotDriver,<sp/>using<sp/>your<sp/>`Action`<sp/>and<sp/>`Observation`<sp/>types<sp/>(see</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">above).</highlight></codeline>
